  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat",
    "add the sliced russian sausage and cook until browned, about 5 minutes",
    "add the shredded cabbage and carrots and cook until slightly tender, about 3-4 minutes",
    "stir in the apple cider vinegar, soy sauce, garlic, and black pepper",
    "cook for an additional 1-2 minutes",
    "serve the stir-fry over a bed of icy slaw, topped with a dollop of sour cream and chopped fresh dill",
    "garnish with additional chopped fresh dill if desired"
